    "After iterative analysis and reflections, the team created major themes illustrating the practical ethical concerns of developing AI for healthcare.",
    "For this publication, the authors present examples of data without identifying information.The researchers' backgrounds informed the interpretation of the data and led to actively developed themes that focus on big ethical questions of who is benefiting from AI and why.",
